Package: expressionSetDF
Type: Package
Title: A simple Bioconductor ExpressionSet-like based on data frames
Version: 0.1.0
Depends: R (>= 4.2.0)
Author: Alex Sanchez
Maintainer: Alex Sanchez Pla <asanchez@ub.edu>
Description: This package provides an implementation of a class similar to ExpressionSet
    The main difference lies in the fact that the "exprs" field is based on a data.frame, instead of a matrix.
    Besides this there is a phenoData and a featureData slots, both data frames as well.  
License: Artistic-2.0
Imports: 
  methods
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
